import React from 'react'
import './Home.css'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css'

function Home () {
    return (
        <main class="border-0 d-flex flex-column justify-content-sm-between">
            <section class="d-flex flex-column col-8">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Fazer pedido</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block m-5">Falar com um consultor</button>
            </section>
        </main>
    )
}

export default Home
